@API(status=STABLE) @FunctionalInterface public interface EnchantmentLevelLangPatch
An API to patch the language file of Minecraft, resource packs and mods.

      Register an extra rendering syntax for enchantment levels.
      Won't be applied without an extension library that invokes EnchantmentLevelLangPatchConfig.setCurrentEnchantmentHooks(xland.mcmod.enchlevellangpatch.api.EnchantmentLevelLangPatch), which modifies current enchantment level patch.
